  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A new technique called Ultrasound-based Acoustic Radiation Force Impulse (ARFI)imaging is
      performed using standard approved ultrasound machines and transducers but the sound waves or
      impulses are produced in a different pattern.  We are going to evaluate the usefulness of
      this new technique in diagnosing different liver conditions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
